This is the rule of BTS Line

1.Red Line(RN) : 20 Baht per Station/ 15 minutes per station

2.Green Line(N) : 40 Baht per station/ 5 minutes per station

3.Pink Line(PK) : 20 Baht per station/ 10 minutes per staion

4.Purple Line(PP) : 15 Baht per staion/ 8 minutes per staion

5.Yellow Line(YL) : 20 Baht per staion/ 15 minutes per station

6.Dark pink Line(RW) : 10 Baht per staion/ 20 minutes

7.Dark purple Line(S) : 15 Baht per station/ 15 minutes per station

8.Blue Line(BL) : 40 Baht per station/ 7 minutes per station

9.Dark green Line(A) : 45 Baht per staion/ 10 minutes per staion

Dashed Line is regular train : 2 Baht per staion/20 minutes per staion
